@Node HIST "The History of this Door..."

  -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
                          History of this Door
  -=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-
   
    Version 1.3 (23rd April 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Now works on Multi-Node BBS's thanks to NSA Designs Patching
       System.

    Version 1.2 (25th March 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Added `Setup New Poll' Section meaning Configuration File format
       had to change to accomodate the New Setup ANSI File.
   O - Removed some Bugs as well as annoying ShareWare Message at the
       End of the Door.
   O - Optimised Code a bit for quicker operation.
    
    Version 1.1 (24th March 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Changed the PowerPOLL License to FreeWare and removed Key-File
       Search Routines.
   O - Also removed the `Registered to' statements.
   O - Corrected some minor bugs in the Graph routine. It drawed one
       extra box than it should of when the Percentage equals 100%.

    Version 1.0 (3rd February 1997)
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Added Graph Options as well as Previous Poll Options.

    Version 0.8 (9th December 1996) - Internal Version Only
    ~~~~~~~~~~~
   O - Corrected Some Major Bugs

